data.description: VA Assumable Loan at 2.25%! Pride of ownership is shown in this stunning home showcasing a spacious 2-car tandem garage PLUS RV garage in Gladden Farms! Discover an exquisite interior offering plenty of natural light, fresh soothing palette, tile flooring, a modern fireplace, & multi-sliders merging the indoor with the outdoor living. The gorgeous chef's kitchen is a cook's delight featuring white shaker cabinets with crown moulding, SS appliances, double wall oven, quartz countertopss, tile backsplash, a walk-in pantry, & a large island with a breakfast bar. Main suite enjoys soft carpet throughout, a private bathroom with dual sinks, make-up vanity, & a walk-in closet. The amazing backyard is an entertainer's dream including a covered patio with an extended Pergola, built-in BBQ, fire and sparkling pool.
